To compile:

GFv3 modules:
cd v3
mvn install --file <module-name>/pom.xml
The jar files are located in <module-name>/target

HK2:
cd hk2
mvn install 

Grizzly:
cd grizzly
mvn install

jsp-api (jsf/mojarra):
cd jsf/mojarra
modify build.properties:  jsf.build.home=SOURCE_HOME where SOURCE_HOME is <glassfish-ri>/jsf
cd jsf/jsf-api
ant -f jsf-api/build.xml
The jsp-api.jar file is located in: <glassfish-ri>/jsf/build/lib/jsf-api.jar